[l] Old and busted: Nazis posten antisemitische Scheisse auf Facebook, kriegen Ärger.New hotness: Der Sohn von Netanjahu postet antisemitische Scheisse auf Facebook, kriegt Ärger.Und zwar nicht, um daran Kritik zu ueben, oder ironisch oder so:Yair Netanyahu, the son of Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu, posted an image on his Facebook page Saturday that seems to suggest a conspiracy is behind his family’s growing legal problems. The meme is laden with anti-Semitic imagery.
